    <h2 slot="heading">
      <span class="h5">Get your home snow ready.</span>
      <span class="h1 enlighten">Improve your <b>insulation</b></span>
    </h2>
    <div slot="paragraph">
        <p>It goes without saying that proper loft insulation is a big part of a warm and an efficient home.</p>
        <p>But you should also think about weatherproofing the gaps around your windows and doors with weather stripping tape – you’ll find it at most DIY stores.</p>
        <p>Or you can use plastic insulation backing on your windows to keep the cold out – and your energy bills down.</p>
    </div>
