    <h2 slot="heading">
      <span class="h5">Get your home snow ready.</span>
      <span class="h1 enlighten">Turn up your <b>thermostat</b></span>
    </h2>
    <div slot="paragraph">
        <p>There’s nothing better than coming back to a warm and cosy home when it’s bitterly cold out. So programme your thermostat to get it winter-ready.</p>
        <p>It’s a good idea to set it to come on for at least part of every day during the chilly season, even if you’re not home. That way, your pipes will be less likely to freeze over and your home won’t get too cold.</p>
    </div>
