      <span class="h5">Get your home snow ready.</span>
      <span class="h1 enlighten"><b>Protect</b> your pipes</span>
    </h2>
    <div slot="paragraph">
        <p>Insulate your pipes with tubing to stop them freezing solid when temperatures fall below zero.</p>
        <p>And don’t forget to fix any leaky taps – even a small trickle can cause a big problem with the weather drops.</p>
