    <h2 slot="heading">
      <span class="h5">Get your home snow ready.</span>
      <span class="h1 enlighten">Check your <b>smoke and carbon monoxide detectors</b></span>
    </h2>
    <div slot="paragraph">
        <p>Did you know there's an increased risk of house fires during cold weather? That’s because more people resort to alternative heat sources like log burners and electric heaters to keep the chill off.</p>
        <p>So it’s vital that you regularly test your smoke alarms and C02 detectors to make sure they’re working properly. And always clear any ventilation outlets after a snowfall to keep them working efficiently.</p>
    </div>
